608
00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:52.000
Kailangan mong mag-resign kung
gusto mo akong ibaba.

609
00:35:52.024 --> 00:35:53.085
So anong gagawin mo?

610
00:35:53.109 --> 00:35:55.045
Ikaw ang nagturo sa akin,

611
00:35:55.069 --> 00:35:57.187
"Mag-home run o strikeout."

612
00:35:57.405 --> 00:35:58.799
Ngayong naka-home run ako,

613
00:35:58.823 --> 00:36:01.775
Masaya akong mag-strikeout.

614
00:36:07.206 --> 00:36:08.791
<i><font color="#ffff00">Naniniwala Kami sa Iyo, Assemblyman Oh</font></i>

615
00:36:17.675 --> 00:36:19.418
pasensya na po.

616
00:36:20.469 --> 00:36:22.072
Ye-jin.

617
00:36:22.096 --> 00:36:25.117
Ang "Masaya" ay binabaybay ng "p."

618
00:36:25.141 --> 00:36:27.301
Ituwid ang "d" na titik.

619
00:36:27.935 --> 00:36:29.538
Okay? Subukan ito.

620
00:36:29.562 --> 00:36:32.499
- Sus, mukhang masaya sila.
- Dito.

621
00:36:32.523 --> 00:36:35.335
- Dito, hayaan mo ako.
- Sige.

622
00:36:35.359 --> 00:36:37.713
Sige.

